Import.code:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from matplotlib.patches import Rectangle

Single.code:
h = '/'
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(1, 1),facecolor="#F7F5F3")
ax.add_patch(Rectangle((0, 0), 2, 2, fill=False, hatch=h))
ax.axis('off')
ax.axis('equal')
plt.title(f"' {h} '");

h = '\\'
